@model ImageCertificate
@{
    this.ViewBag.Title = "Certificates";
}

<h2 class="text-center">Info</h2>
<div class="text-center ">
    <p class="text-justify col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
        After a specialty is completed, you can archive certificate like this. You should prove that you deserve this certificate.
        First of all send a candidature for your favorite specialty. If you already done this, next check your courses. There are
        several tasks and tests. Complete them and check your marks for courses. If you have studied hard you may be rewarded with
        a certificate. Then you can show the people that you are guru for this specialty and easily find a job.
        <br />
        <b>Good luck!</b> 
    </p>
    <img alt="Embedded Image" src="data:image/png;base64,@(Convert.ToBase64String(Model.Data))" width="450" />
</div>
